## Common Patterns to Follow

### Assignment Management
- Use AssignmentContext for state management
- Support all question types (multiple-choice, numerical, open-response, essay)
- Implement proper grading workflows
- Track student progress and analytics

### Question Bank Integration
- Use QuestionBankContext for centralized question management
- Organize questions by physics units and lessons
- Support advanced filtering and search
- Track question usage analytics

### Vocabulary Games
- Use VocabularyContext for game state
- Implement consistent game mechanics
- Support multiple game types (hangman, matching, word shoot, etc.)
- Track student progress and scores

### Student Activity Tracking
- Use StudentActivityContext for progress monitoring
- Implement comprehensive analytics
- Support lesson and assignment tracking
- Provide teacher dashboards

Remember: This is an educational application focused on physics learning. Always prioritize educational effectiveness, accessibility, and student engagement in your code decisions.
